        "data": "<h2>Add</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase support to 15 SSL Certs per environment</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Disable email verification in DXP 7.3 non-production environments</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span>Bugs</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Attempting to delete service through console was returning 404 error</li>\n<li>Logs page was not loading for multiple projects</li>\n</ul>"
